            var i = 0;
            var ulist = '<ul>';

            $xml.find("item").each(function () {
                var $this = $(this),
                    item = {
                        title: $this.find("title").text().replace("<![CDATA[", "").replace("]]>", ""),

                        guid: $this.find("guid ").text()
                    }
                i++;
                ulist += '<li><a target="_blank" href="' + item.link + '">' + item.title + '</a></li>';
            });

            ulist += '</ul>';
            
            if (i > 0) {
                $("#disturbancesTickerContent").html(ulist);
            }
            else {
                $("#disturbancesTicker").hide();
            }

            brail.hTicker.init();
        }).fail(function () {
            $("#disturbancesTicker").hide();
        });

    });

<script>

    $(document).ready(function () {

        var feedUrl = '/RssFeedProxies/HIM.aspx?lang=NL';

        $.get(feedUrl, function (data) {
            var $xml = $($.parseXML(data));

            var ulist = '<ul>';
            var i = 0;
            var maxItems = 3;

            $xml.find("item").each(function () {
                var $this = $(this),
                    item = {
                        title: $this.find("title").text().replace("<![CDATA[", "").replace("]]>", ""),
                        link: $this.find("link").text(),
                        description: $this.find("description").text().replace("<![CDATA[", "").replace("]]>", ""),
                        pubDate: $this.find("pubDate").text(),
                        guid: $this.find("guid ").text()
                    }
                i++;

                if (i <= maxItems) {

                    var maxLengtTitleCharacters = 42;
                    var maxLengthTitle = item.title;
                    if (maxLengthTitle.length > maxLengtTitleCharacters)
                        maxLengthTitle = maxLengthTitle.substring(0, maxLengtTitleCharacters) + '...';
                    ulist += '<li class="feed-item arrow js-ellipsis multiline" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 4px;"><a target="_blank" href="' + item.link + '">' + maxLengthTitle + '</a></li>';
                }

            })

            ulist += '</ul>';

            $("#networkDisturbanceLink").html('Storingen op het net');
            //$("#countFeed").html('(' + i.toString() + ')');

            $("#feedTitleLabel").html('Storingen op het net' + ' (' + i.toString() + ')');

            $("#disturbancesTickerContent2").html(ulist);
        }).fail(function () {
            $("#networkDisturbanceFeed").hide();
        });

    });



</script>
